    "causal_summary": "The v1.0.2 stress rerun showed strong remediation progress, but the next optimization frontier is cross-system search quality rather than single-cell closure. The memory, code graph, skill advisor, CocoIndex, causal graph, and RAG composition paths each expose useful signals, but the system lacks a unified optimization plan for precision, recall, p95 latency, citation trust, degraded readiness, and learned fusion.",
